AND

$718

OF THESE CHARGES WERE RECORDED IN COST OF PRODUCTS SOLD FOR THE YEARS ENDED

JUNE 30, 2017

AND

2016

, RESPECTIVELY.  THE REMAINDER OF THE CHARGES WERE INCLUDED IN NET EARNINGS FROM DISCONTINUED OPERATIONS.  OF THE TOTAL COSTS INCURRED SINCE THE INCEPTION OF THIS RESTRUCTURING PROGRAM,

